# SkillForge Complete Environment Map

## Frontend Environment (.env in /frontend)
# Required for Clerk Authentication
VITE_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_...

## Backend Environment (.env in /backend)
# Required for Gemini Skill Extraction
GEMINI_API_KEY=AIzaSy...

# Optional: Supabase Credentials if testing DB persistence
SUPABASE_URL=https://...
SUPABASE_KEY=ey...

# Optional: YouTube API Key if switching from simulated to live data fetches
YOUTUBE_API_KEY=AI...

# System Flags
ENVIRONMENT=development
TF_CPP_MIN_LOG_LEVEL=3
TF_ENABLE_ONEDNN_OPTS=0
